        <br />
        <h1>Cancellations</h1>
        Cancellations must be made 6 hours in advance of your lesson time by text or email. Under <strong>6 hours</strong>
        you will lose the lesson fee. Last-minute cancellations are excused only with valid reason.

        I am flexible with schedule changes to match work or school schedules with advance notice and upon availability.

        If you are having technical difficulties or your video is blurry or lagging, I will reschedule the lesson to give
        you another chance to ensure your equipment is ready. Back-to-back lessons with technical difficulties will result
        in a cancellation and loss of lesson fee.

        I will only wait 15 minutes online during our scheduled time. After <strong>15 minutes</strong> I will consider you
        a no-show and you will lose the lesson fee. You may notify by text or email any delays and I can extend my time
        (depending on availability).
        <br />
        <h1>Payments and Refunds</h1>
        All payments are made through my booking page on Setmore.com.

        Any requested refunds must be made <strong>6 hours</strong> before the scheduled session & will take approximately 5
        – 10 days to process.
